[SN]TITLE[SN]
Kevan Hurst: Mansfield Town midfielder joins Guiseley on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
National League side Guiseley have signed Mansfield midfielder Kevan Hurst on loan until the end of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Hurst joined Mansfield in June after being released by Southend, and has made 16 appearances for the League Two side this season.
The 31-year-old former Sheffield United trainee had not started in a league game since 17 December.
He could make his debut for Guiseley when they travel to Wrexham in the National League on Saturday.
